data.value:
Welcome to our application. To use it, you must first select a DATASET, the country or countries whose data you are interested in, and the data period.
To obtain the result, press the "REFRESH" button. After a while, your graph will be displayed.
You can also select an interactive map: animated maps are opened in your browser by default, while others are displayed on the application screen.
The "RESET" button resets everything if you only want to display one map.
